        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Homeowners in Bankruptcy Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill increases the homestead exemption an individual debtor can claim in a bankruptcy to $100,000. The homestead exemption allows a debtor to exempt from property of the estate the debtor's interest in property used as the debtor's residence or interest in a burial plot for the debtor.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
